    "caption_text": "AARON LEVINE x ZARA\n\nAaron P. Levine @aaronplevine has been captivated by clothing since the age of four. As a child, he would arrange pieces on the floor, experimenting with colors, textures, and fabrics—never with the intention of wearing them, but simply to observe the dialogue they created together. \n\nOver the years, he has honed an instinctive mastery for blending items across diverse product categories, assembling looks that feel at once rooted in tradition and refreshingly unexpected. Tailored garments, technical outerwear, denim, knitwear, and trekking boots converge effortlessly under his eye, forming functional, considered outfits suited to virtually any setting.\n\nFor him, this practice is more than a craft; it is a lifelong devotion—his profession, and his passion.\n\n#zara #zaraman #aaronlevine",
